
--------------------- Misc. formatting commands -------------------

  ,PP        Paragraph
  ,PPNL N    Paragraph need N lines on same page
  ,PPSP N    Paragraph space N lines
  ,PPSI N    Paragraph single indent

  ,BFS  N    Boldface strike N times at printout

  ,PADC C    Pad character C for non-paddable spaces on printout
  ,MMC  C    Mail Merge character C
  ,PC   C    Print character C for delimiting print strings


  ,*         Comment line
